caption.body: NOW PLAYING: Filmmaker Anthony Florez examines native identity through the eyes of self-professed cowgirl Kellie Harry, a fellow member of the Pyramid Lake Paiute Tribe who returned to Northern Nevada to raise her children in their traditional lifestyle.  See "Generations" by Anthony Florez, now playing in the Video Arts Room located pre-security in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/33lZL7Y
